<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<form class="post" action="/posts" method="POST">
    <h2>Enter Title:</h2>
    <input type="text" name="title">
    <h2>Insert YouTube Link:</h2>
    <input type="text" name="video">
    <h2>Enter Description:</h2>
    <textarea name="description"></textarea>
    <button type="submit">Create New Post</button>
</form>

<article class="text">
    <h1>Instructions For a Good Post</h1>
    <h2>Title:</h2>
    <p>Make a title that quickly describes the problem</p>
    <h2>Video Link:</h2>
    <p>For entering your YouTube link make sure to follow the steps below.<br><i>Don't use the link in the address bar!</i></p>
    <div class="imgs">
        <img id="step1" src="https://i.imgur.com/BwLAgZ4.png">
        <img id="step2" src="https://i.imgur.com/1CYweZF.png">
    </div>
    <h2>Description:</h2>
    <p>
        The description is important! Try to pinpoint exactly what you're having trouble with and where on the climb you are having the issue.<br> 
        Vague descriptions will make it difficult for other users to give you constructive criticism. Also consider adding the name of the climb and possibly the Mountain Project link.
    </p>
</article>


